{"tid":2486230,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"[#Mon#Monitor] 電腦螢幕集中討論#62","createTime":"2021-04-12T18:04:57.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-15T07:39:25.000Z","uid":73626,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"0a7c9565b3100b57c7a6fc8fc23a3f73f4756af8","tid":2486230,"uid":73626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-12T18:04:57.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\">Newegg/AOC/Philips為中資公司</span><br />\n<br />\n不想自行做功課, 只求快想省時間,<br />\n對研究螢幕一點興趣都沒有的求推薦文,<br />\n個人看到一律會跳過<br />\n<br />\n總之, 推薦文的話, 就請期待其他網友幫忙吧<br />\n<br />\n除非有看到做功課做很多的香港網友, 問出有水準的問題<br />\n個人也許還會回答, 但應該只會是極少數.<br />\n偶而才來看看, 基本上也不用期待<br />\n<br />\n香港的螢幕規格表暫時還有在幫忙更新,<br />\n<br />\n但現在也該是時候出現下一個,<br />\n像多鮫魚巴打一樣的香港人物了吧..<br />\n<br />\n星河電腦螢幕資訊分享站<br />\n<a href=\"https://sites.google.com/view/twmonitors/首頁\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsites.google.com%2Fview%2Ftwmonitors%2F%E9%A6%96%E9%A0%81&d=2BCMh5porRb4XQq0U%2Bi1DAQPoALeJAOsJ3HVvkpnkS8%3D&h=a2216200\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://sites.google.com/view/twmonitors/首頁</a><br />\n<br />\n多多查看網站學習做功課, 親自思考自己要買什麼樣的產品.<br />\n<br />\n其中幾個表格就算香港地區也應有相當的參考度<br />\n<br />\n香港版144HZ/21:9/2K/4K螢幕規格表連結<br />\n<a href=\"https://sites.google.com/view/twmonitors/查看表格/香港地區專頁\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsites.google.com%2Fview%2Ftwmonitors%2F%E6%9F%A5%E7%9C%8B%E8%A1%A8%E6%A0%BC%2F%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%9C%B0%E5%8D%80%E5%B0%88%E9%A0%81&d=2BCMh5porRb4XQq0U%2Bi1DAQPoALeJAOsJ3HVvkpnkS8%3D&h=90c2eaab\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://sites.google.com/view/twmonitors/查看表格/香港地區專頁</a><br />\n<br />\n香港地區販賣的螢幕產品規格表, 有對應的價錢方便比價<br />\n<br />\n2019同步總評表<br />\n<a href=\"https://sites.google.com/view/twmonitors/年度大賞/2019總評表不定期更新\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsites.google.com%2Fview%2Ftwmonitors%2F%E5%B9%B4%E5%BA%A6%E5%A4%A7%E8%B3%9E%2F2019%E7%B8%BD%E8%A9%95%E8%A1%A8%E4%B8%8D%E5%AE%9A%E6%9C%9F%E6%9B%B4%E6%96%B0&d=2BCMh5porRb4XQq0U%2Bi1DAQPoALeJAOsJ3HVvkpnkS8%3D&h=2dc3758c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://sites.google.com/view/twmonitors/年度大賞/2019總評表不定期更新</a><br />\n<br />\n無限預算推薦表<br />\n<a href=\"https://sites.google.com/view/twmonitors/查看表格/無限預算推薦表\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsites.google.com%2Fview%2Ftwmonitors%2F%E6%9F%A5%E7%9C%8B%E8%A1%A8%E6%A0%BC%2F%E7%84%A1%E9%99%90%E9%A0%90%E7%AE%97%E6%8E%A8%E8%96%A6%E8%A1%A8&d=2BCMh5porRb4XQq0U%2Bi1DAQPoALeJAOsJ3HVvkpnkS8%3D&h=34d097ee\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://sites.google.com/view/twmonitors/查看表格/無限預算推薦表</a><br />\n<br />\n低價高CP推薦表<br />\n<a href=\"https://sites.google.com/view/twmonitors/查看表格/低價高cp推薦表\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsites.google.com%2Fview%2Ftwmonitors%2F%E6%9F%A5%E7%9C%8B%E8%A1%A8%E6%A0%BC%2F%E4%BD%8E%E5%83%B9%E9%AB%98cp%E6%8E%A8%E8%96%A6%E8%A1%A8&d=2BCMh5porRb4XQq0U%2Bi1DAQPoALeJAOsJ3HVvkpnkS8%3D&h=dd06edc5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://sites.google.com/view/twmonitors/查看表格/低價高cp推薦表</a><br />\n<br />\n多鮫魚電腦螢幕知識分享站<br />\n<a href=\"https://sites.google.com/view/monitor101/首頁\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsites.google.com%2Fview%2Fmonitor101%2F%E9%A6%96%E9%A0%81&d=2BCMh5porRb4XQq0U%2Bi1DAQPoALeJAOsJ3HVvkpnkS8%3D&h=8ec32c46\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://sites.google.com/view/monitor101/首頁</a><br />\n<br />\n這個則是多鮫魚巴打(1~10帖作者)整理出來的網頁<br />\n有推薦清單跟一些知識部分, 也具有參考性.<br />\n<br />\n香港螢幕報價表<br />\n<a href=\"https://goo.gl/dN1MKA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FdN1MKA&d=2BCMh5porRb4XQq0U%2Bi1DAQPoALeJAOsJ3HVvkpnkS8%3D&h=904a8fe4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/dN1MKA</a><br />\n<br />\n為了讓更多港友知道最新價格與價錢透明化, 多鮫魚巴打建議有查到價錢報價的, 寫到共用表格上, 讓港友都能進行更詳細的價錢比較<br />\n(據說Price hk價錢更新過慢)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nBest 144hz-240hz Monitors (NCX's Ranking)<br />\n<a href=\"http://web.archive.org/web/20170926175434/http://wecravegamestoo.com:80/forums/monitor-reviews-discussion/15713-best-144hz-240hz-monitors.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fweb.archive.org%2Fweb%2F20170926175434%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fwecravegamestoo.com%3A80%2Fforums%2Fmonitor-reviews-discussion%2F15713-best-144hz-240hz-monitors.html&d=2BCMh5porRb4XQq0U%2Bi1DAQPoALeJAOsJ3HVvkpnkS8%3D&h=274681f1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://web.archive.org/web/20170926175434/http://wecravegamestoo.com:80/forums/monitor-reviews-discussion/15713-best-144hz-240hz-monitors.html</a><br />\n<br />\n英文不錯也可以去看看NCX之前的144Hz排行帖內容<br />\n另外推薦港友多多參考<br />\n<br />\n&quot;香港格價網&quot; Price HK的價錢還有店家資訊<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.price.com.hk/category.php?c=100024\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.price.com.hk%2Fcategory.php%3Fc%3D100024&d=2BCMh5porRb4XQq0U%2Bi1DAQPoALeJAOsJ3HVvkpnkS8%3D&h=5925d9d0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.price.com.hk/category.php?c=100024</a><br />\n<br />\n想買哪一款螢幕不知道哪裡有在賣, 有沒有現貨,<br />\n可以查看這個網站, 然後打電話聯絡店家進行詢問.<br />\n<br />\n基本注意事項<br />\n1. IPS/VA/TN差距為何很重要, 請自行爬文研究.<br />\n2. 4K遊戲, 顯示卡2080或以上才有資格跑, 顯示卡差只能降解析度跑<br />\n3. 看影片, 沒有50%時間以上都玩競技型(FPS/賽車)遊戲, TN直接淘汰, 選VA or IPS<br />\n4. PS4/PS4 Pro/Switch不支援2k輸出, 只支援FHD, 顯示到2k螢幕會需放大較模糊些, 優先選擇FHD產品<br />\n5. 4K + TN螢幕, 全部都是垃圾, 不需考慮.<br />\n6. TN + 60hz產品,不具參考價值.<br />\n7. HDR10=格式，HDR400-1400=認證。目前主流HDR資源都係HDR10格式 市面上HDR MON HDR10性能有高有低 所以VESA 搞左個displayHDR認證<br />\n分為HDR400/500/600/1000/1400 另外仲有UHD premium認證 大概等同HDR1000 冇任何認證會只標支援HDR10"},{"pid":"00cceca9894d6e3eeab2b18a6ce25f684b296c47","tid":2486230,"uid":73626,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-12T18:05:35.000Z","msg":"建議 LIST<br />\n2K 144HZ VG27AQL1A / XG279Q<br />\n4K 60HZ VG289Q<br />\n4K 144HZ XG27UQ / 27GN950-B<br />\n<br />\nDisplay Port 1.4 線<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://shop.hornington.com/products/j5create-jdc43-8k-displayport-cable-2m\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fshop.hornington.com%2Fproducts%2Fj5create-jdc43-8k-displayport-cable-2m&d=2BCMh5porRb4XQq0U%2Bi1DAQPoALeJAOsJ3HVvkpnkS8%3D&h=ba0ed08d\" target=\"_blank\">https://shop.hornington.com/products/j5create-jdc43-8k-displayport-cable-2m</a>"},{"pid":"e88c4c24a727e8d83d4028d691a18ec2c00e6879","tid":2486230,"uid":73626,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-12T18:06:17.000Z","msg":"睇完星河 暫時睇中XG2405 想知有冇伏<br />\n想要內置喇叭144Hz 24-25吋 2個hdmi位<br />\n主要睇youtube同駁ps4打下fps<br />\n2k內有冇更好選擇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a670dc6c47197f8b60229c3b917f9bfcd810afa2","tid":2486230,"uid":259400,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"e88c4c24a727e8d83d4028d691a18ec2c00e6879","tid":2486230,"uid":73626,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-12T18:06:17.000Z","msg":"睇完星河 暫時睇中XG2405 想知有冇伏<br />\n想要內置喇叭144Hz 24-25吋 2個hdmi位<br />\n主要睇youtube同駁ps4打下fps<br />\n2k內有冇更好選擇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-12T19:35:12.000Z","msg":"PS4 output到144Hz?"},{"pid":"110fec033f44c5498b5e37c52c9dc2280012c48b","tid":2486230,"uid":259400,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-12T19:47:55.000Z","msg":"話說有無啲 4K mon <br />\n普通睇野行4K 60Hz <br />\n打機就行 2K 144Hz <br />\n咁樣會唔會平啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4ec8dcd6eaddf593a25a345f97d532a0216d863","tid":2486230,"uid":56146,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-12T20:08:16.000Z","msg":"請問吓巴打知唔知lg27gn950係咪全港都未返貨？<br />\n訂咗開頭話4月頭有，依家話唔知幾時有貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"385b3599a2f56c067f4a9df31a86754294658711","tid":2486230,"uid":37407,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T01:23:41.000Z","msg":"想問下如果1070夠唔夠力推1隻27 2k 144加多隻普通24 2k<br />\n27果隻睇岩MSI Optix G27CQ4<br />\n隻144主要攞黎打csgo/其他fps, 都會攞黎睇下netflix同打下ps4<br />\n雙mon就主要工作需要,所以另一隻冇乜特別要求<br />\n求指教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff241bf399d5c5c5f6e55eb04d45ca756e95a4c5","tid":2486230,"uid":3290,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T01:38:07.000Z","msg":"挑選方向 by <strong><span class=\"blue\">是旦啦吊</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/sGuyGsX\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/sGuyGsX</a><br />\n<br />\n1.不直 唔洗講啦 一分錢一分貨<br />\n2.用途 文書 睇片 畫圖 打機(打咩驚呀? FPS? 3A RPG?)<br />\n<br />\n睇片:正路就4K,想要HDR 入場費就一萬 唔要最平3000蚊已經有交易<br />\n打機:FHD 2K 4K 都有,打PVP驚正路就配埋高Hz (144/240Hz,越高Hz越流暢)<br />\nFHD144就2000到<br />\n2K144/240 3000-6000<br />\n4k144 7000起<br />\n3.長闊比 正路就16:9 21:9就闊D,投入感會多啲<br />\n32:9 冷門D<br />\n4. 面板類型:正路就ips&gt;va&gt;tn(最好唔好)<br />\n<br />\n有多少少目標同認識再問啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2k高Hz(大勢所趨): M27Q MAG274QRF-QD VG279QM G7<br />\n其他熱門項目: vg289q g34wqc u2720q ew3270u"},{"pid":"d4249120344382c196b83ddda59ec01fcb3ad319","tid":2486230,"uid":3290,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T01:41:05.000Z","msg":"今日蘋果講螢幕臂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/lifestyle/20210413/3LMLQHV5QNCR5LBNVXRTVUDMBM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2F20210413%2F3LMLQHV5QNCR5LBNVXRTVUDMBM%2F&d=2BCMh5porRb4XQq0U%2Bi1DAQPoALeJAOsJ3HVvkpnkS8%3D&h=5d10b116\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2F20210413%2F3LMLQHV5QNCR5LBNVXRTVUDMBM%2F&h=b858c687\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/lifestyle/20210413/3LMLQHV5QNCR5LBNVXRTVUDMBM/</a>"},{"pid":"2369155b0906dd0f6f64400c0335873082f7cacf","tid":2486230,"uid":79829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"110fec033f44c5498b5e37c52c9dc2280012c48b","tid":2486230,"u